column2: SELECT s.plate, s.fiberid, s.mjd, ga.oiii_#_flux, ga.oiii_#_flux_err, (sph.modelmag_g-sph.modelmag_r) as col_g_r,    sph.modelmag_g-#*log1#(#E+#*sph.z)+# as M_g, (sph.modelmag_u-sph.modelmag_r) as col_u_r,   sph.modelmag_r-#*log1#(#E+#*sph.z)+# as M_r, sph.subClass    INTO mydb.tremonti_delibro  FROM GalSpecLine as ga, specobj as s, Galaxy as g, SpecPhoto as sph    WHERE ga.oiii_#_flux > #*ga.oiii_#_flux_err   AND ga.h_gamma_flux > #*ga.h_gamma_flux_err   AND ga.h_gamma_flux > #*ga.oiii_#_flux   AND s.class = &&&   AND s.specobjid = g.specobjid    AND s.specobjid = ga.specobjid   AND sph.specobjid = g.specobjid   AND sph.specobjid = ga.specobjid   AND ga.oiii_#_flux_err > #   AND g.specobjid > #   AND sph.z > #
